{"tid":26821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范太：料今屆特首選戰難以君子之爭","createTime":"2016-12-07T03:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T08:59:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30478b24aae967ea8c4e5ee19c43d242c21afde5","tid":26821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委范徐麗泰出席電台節目時指，財政司長曾俊華在立法會拒答4名議員提問影響政府形象，令人感覺政府內部溝通不暢順，又指對臨近特首選舉「有啲擔心」，認為難以是君子之爭。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰指作為旁觀者，認為特首梁振英和兩位司長的說法都可能是事實，但會令人政府團隊溝通「唔暢順」；她指政府的立場是認為4位議員宣誓不成立，但因立法會秘書長已接受有關宣誓，不論建制或非建議員都認為他們有權提答，故認為林鄭在信中指，為立法會運作暢順而接受4位議員提問的說法「最正路」。<br />\n<br />\n她又指曾俊華已表明沒被人跣，「無理由懷疑佢嘅說話」，對於現象是否屬特首選舉前哨戰，范直言「有啲擔心」，因上一屆特首選舉算不上君子之爭，認為如美國大選那樣的抹黑和謠言會四起，「而家興丫嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n對於中央政府對下屆特首的立場，范徐麗泰認為梁振英處理兩年前佔領行動的表現，獲國家主席習近平以「疾風知勁草，板蕩識忠臣」評價，是過往未曾試過；她希望中央不只有一個特首人選，有兩個較好，但三個或會流選，她相信今次特首選舉難以是君子之爭。"},{"pid":"aab9f98f774d9392752e69755f74c5b867d51ff8","tid":26821,"uid":44982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"屌 呀媽係女人<br />\n有梁振英點會有君子之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b35e8e27b07bb1a7024a6d8ee0fb75e9a88140","tid":26821,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 呀媽係女人<br />\n有梁振英點會有君子之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到上屆選舉好君子咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6763eb805d3d2cf8c2fe1ee58dc717c459ca7b4","tid":26821,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 呀媽係女人<br />\n有梁振英點會有君子之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到上屆選舉好君子咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國大選最君子"},{"pid":"d41f59d804b0ccc828b143cab309390047106112","tid":26821,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"葉劉係女人<br />\n梗係唔係君子之爭"},{"pid":"7186a2f18ec301c300f34a7edb9608f0317c0a17","tid":26821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014162&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014162%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&d=oDXEYGnpFcyUeXg9UHvZKJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7bd07e0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014162%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&h=2784aa64\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014162&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207</a>"},{"pid":"e0ba21754c1f864bdead5a0a6adb37621564687a","tid":26821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}